 No because 
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{x}$
\end_inset

 doesn't belong to the convex hull of 
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{x}^{1}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{x}^{2}$
